  "body": "To reproduce:\r\n\r\n1. Post a message that includes a GitHub URL pointing to a specific issue\r\n2. Watch the URL get unfurled after the message is posted\r\n3. Edit the previously posted message to change the GitHub URL to point to a different issue.\r\n\r\nCurrent incorrect behaviour: the unfurled URL doesn't update, and displays the URL that was posted prior to the message edit.\r\n\r\nCorrect desired behaviour: the unfurled URL display should update to show the new URL after the message is edited.  After any message is edited, any URLs that were unfurled as a result of that message should be refreshed so that if for instance the URL is deleted from the message the unfurled URL should disappear or if the URL is changed the unfurled URL should update. ",
